Richard Procter is a students graduate of the class of 2010 at UC Davis. He was the 20082009 editor in chief of The California Aggie. He served as campus editor during the 20072008 school year and was a campus writer during the 20062007 school year. After interning at the San Francisco Chronicle, he returned to the Aggie for his senior year as a sportswriter, covering the UC Davis football team and mens basketball team.

He is currently a student at the Columbia Graduate School of Journalism and will graduate in May 2011 with a masters degree in digital media.
